ComicInfo.Summary:
The Castle on the Edge of Infinity is collapsing, and the last of its mysteries is fading from the universe forever. Gina gears up for one last expedition into the ancient cosmic halls! It's on the way to the exit, so what's the harm in taking a look, right? Britanny knows where Gina's going, and she doesn't like it one bit. Gina's heading for the final resting place of Gloriana Jones...to say goodbye. There's got to be a way to talk Gina out of this!
Right?
